{"tid":2433873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「初選群組直播三日後記」","createTime":"2021-03-05T07:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T10:55:17.000Z","uid":11055,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2f0b7a607c765f73a5622f56e947399dffda11e2","tid":2433873,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"對唔住，本來應承左你地會嚟足咁多日，<br />\n但係第2日我真係頂唔順係屋企訓足20個鐘。<br />\n最多出返嚟我請食飯？<br />\n<br />\n尋晚情緒好差，結果冇同各位連登巴絲交代最後判決嘅事情。<br />\n不過我相信好多在場嘅直播師都有同大家講，<br />\n但係我都同大家交代下：<br />\n法庭裁決第8，10，11，14，16，17，20，24，26，28，30，40，42，43，46被告批準保釋，<br />\n律政司刑事檢控專員隨即引用《刑事訴訟程序條例》9I條作出上訴，15名獲準保釋之被告隨時還押，案件將於48小時內轉介高等法院審理。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲/香港人繼續關注保釋案件同時，唔好忘記其餘32人，<br />\n呢一單案，本來就係無中生有，<br />\n佢地冇一個係應該被控。<br />\n<br />\n回頭一望，本來大家仲投訴緊選舉冇人性、日做廿粒鐘、成日比藍絲屌、黑狗日日踩場、唔好搞我啲義工......<br />\n轉眼間，我地由街站日日互相取笑皮膚又差左，黑眼圈就嚟大過隻眼，<br />\n變到要隔住個Mon，望住你地企係塊玻璃後面。<br />\n由一齊搵地方匿埋食煙，驚比街坊見到，<br />\n到你地還押，驚你地冇啖好食。<br />\n我之後會多啲探你地....<br />\n<br />\n以前讀書，總覺得歷史只係一個又一個故事，<br />\n到今日我地親身經歷，並由自己書寫，<br />\n先驚覺歷史之沉重。<br />\n<br />\n寫得好亂，又唔知應該擺去邊到，<br />\n唯有寄之以連登，多謝各位巴絲，<br />\n徐巴打跪求各位，<br />\n片刻不忘，即使千秋過後，<br />\n都要將呢段歷史傳落去比我地每一個後代。"},{"pid":"6daacac1351a3ee800492c3eb2e8180157f57df7","tid":2433873,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9676edc0d8636185be4ab9035ce4a32ee3352baf","tid":2433873,"uid":185793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:25:07.000Z","msg":"多謝你，take care"},{"pid":"eedc24839108113d57f55e943ab54b60609ff478","tid":2433873,"uid":243656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c719e96fda4b2dc1c5ed6476997cdc75282ff8f4","tid":2433873,"uid":30000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:15:47.000Z","msg":"巴打我撐住你 呢幾日好多謝你"},{"pid":"0964d3a1a54a8f03821aca69c92a004ada0755e5","tid":2433873,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eedc24839108113d57f55e943ab54b60609ff478","tid":2433873,"uid":243656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b635665805832b6884be3f2a7c010694ccb9c1bd","tid":2433873,"uid":271367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"多謝徐巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab765a3f168d5fa6e010e94d68e71c078592865","tid":2433873,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}